headline.print_headline: Cuomo Defends Handling of Corruption Panel
headline.main: Cuomo Defends Handling of Corruption Panel

lead_paragraph: Gov. Andrew Cuomo on Monday defended his handling of an anti-corruption commission, dismissing reports that his administration interfered with its work.
